headline: Intuit Extends Ecosystem With Career Pipeline And Checkr Integration Insights
summary: Intuit (NasdaqGS:INTU) launched its Career Pipeline Program for accounting students, aimed at expanding training and support for future accountants. The company also announced an integration with Checkr that brings background checks directly into QuickBooks Payroll and Intuit Enterprise Suite. These updates are positioned to address talent development and compliance workflows for accounting and HR teams using Intuit products.
